{"1000030":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Cook, Serve, Delicious! 3?!","steam_appid":1000030,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[1231250],"detailed_description":"<h1>Giant Bomb Game of the Year<\/h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/extras\/GB2020GOTY.png?t=1745434271\" \/><\/p><br><h1>GameMaker Awards Best Game<\/h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/extras\/GMA2020Awards_copy.png?t=1745434271\" \/><\/p><br><h1>关于游戏<\/h1><strong>NOTE: This game is in English only.<\/strong><br><br>故事背景设置在 2042 年，饱受战火蹂躏的美国本土已彻底改变了面貌。在主线故事的引领下，你将完整体验到一段全新的剧情章节，并在此期间烹饪数百种食物——其中包括多种本作新增的食物——与挑战数百个关卡。这些完全重新设计的关卡采用全新结构的游戏方式，将让你的游玩过程充满紧张感与刺激感。除此之外，你也可以随时开启与关闭本作中新增的休闲模式（Chill Mode），让自己轻松愉快地烹饪美食！<br><br>- 可单人或与好友在单机合作模式下（支持随时中途加入或退出）游玩剧情章节。<br>- 使用多种能改变你游戏方式的配件来升级餐车！<br>- 超过 200 种食物供你扩展美食目录！<br>- 用样式各异的小饰品装点你的餐车！<br>- 包括动作设置、闪光\/频闪设置、音频与色盲功能在内的大量无障碍游戏功能。<br>- 游戏拥有超过 380 个关卡，可提供一百小时以上的游戏时长！<br>- 曾经荣获大奖（IndieCade Audio of the Year，2020）的游戏原声带，由 Jonathan Geer（Owlboy）创作！<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/extras\/teaserbanner.png?t=1745434271\" \/>","about_the_game":"<strong>NOTE: This game is in English only.<\/strong><br><br>故事背景设置在 2042 年，饱受战火蹂躏的美国本土已彻底改变了面貌。在主线故事的引领下，你将完整体验到一段全新的剧情章节，并在此期间烹饪数百种食物——其中包括多种本作新增的食物——与挑战数百个关卡。这些完全重新设计的关卡采用全新结构的游戏方式，将让你的游玩过程充满紧张感与刺激感。除此之外，你也可以随时开启与关闭本作中新增的休闲模式（Chill Mode），让自己轻松愉快地烹饪美食！<br><br>- 可单人或与好友在单机合作模式下（支持随时中途加入或退出）游玩剧情章节。<br>- 使用多种能改变你游戏方式的配件来升级餐车！<br>- 超过 200 种食物供你扩展美食目录！<br>- 用样式各异的小饰品装点你的餐车！<br>- 包括动作设置、闪光\/频闪设置、音频与色盲功能在内的大量无障碍游戏功能。<br>- 游戏拥有超过 380 个关卡，可提供一百小时以上的游戏时长！<br>- 曾经荣获大奖（IndieCade Audio of the Year，2020）的游戏原声带，由 Jonathan Geer（Owlboy）创作！<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/extras\/teaserbanner.png?t=1745434271\" \/>","short_description":"销量高达百万的系列游戏现已推出续作！在这款“量大管饱”的游戏中，你将穿越经受战火蹂躏的美国，烹饪餐品、提供菜肴并管理你的餐车，为人们奉献数百种风味各异的美食！","supported_languages":"英语<strong>*<\/strong><br><strong>*<\/strong>具有完全音频支持的语言","reviews":"“Cook, Serve, Delicious! 3?! takes the best of the first two games and brings so much more with better progression, more food, accessibility options, and more to be the ultimate cooking game. I already loved the first Cook, Serve, Delicious! game and while the second entry was a step forward in many ways, it also regressed. Cook, Serve, Delicious! 3?! is everything I wanted from this franchise and more.”<br>4.5\/5 – Touch Arcade<br><br>“Cook Serve Delicious 3 is a stressful, yet at times relaxing, cooking game. It is so close to being perfect that I can't wait to see what the next iteration brings.”<br>8\/10 – PC Invasion<br><br>“A relentless and strategic kitchen management game, Cook, Serve, Delicious! 3?! rewards hard effort with moments of transcendental clarity, when plates start flowing and everything is slotting into place. It is meditation. I have never felt a greater sense of peace and purpose than when rolling six burritos in less than five seconds. Prescribe it to people who have lost their way.”<br>Rock Paper Shotgun<br>","header_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/header.jpg?t=1745434271","capsule_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/96671a66567b407c383fe5e84ecb81f0960b1dbd\/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1745434271","capsule_imagev5":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1000030\/96671a66567b407c383fe5e84ecb81f0960b1dbd\/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1745434271","website":"http:\/\/www.cookservedelicious.com","pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>最低配置:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>操作系统 *:<\/strong> Windows  7\/8\/10+<br><\/li><li><strong>内存:<\/strong> 4 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>显卡:<\/stron